================
Forum Censorship
================

This module enables you to censor specific phrases (e.g. swear words) on forums.

Usage
=====

#. go to Website Admin -> Forum -> Censorship;
#. specify phrases.

.. image:: https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas
   :alt: Try me on Runbot
   :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/186/9.0

Known issues / Roadmap
======================

* Censor phrases for a specific forum.
* There is no check on recursion (one replacement gets replaced by another).
* There is no check on phrase uniqueness.
* Add option to obstruct creation of forum post.

